1.title: The Forest Attacks!

episode of.title: The Mysteries of Alfred Hedgehog (TV Series 2010– )

1.plot: Milo refuses to run a race because he thinks he was attacked by something in the forest. It turns out it's the Gorse bush which pops and ejects seeds in hot weather.

2.title: The Sleepless Night

episode of.title: The Mysteries of Alfred Hedgehog (TV Series 2010– )

2.plot: No one is getting sleep because a tree has been cut down, a tapping noise is heard and water is flooding the forest. It's the beaver who moved his damn.

4.title: Stranger Among Us

episode of.title: The Mysteries of Alfred Hedgehog (TV Series 2010– )

4.plot: A famous rabbit, Ricardo, won't sing at the town festival because his fur has changed color. It turns out, he's a snowshoe rabbit and his fur turns from white to brown with the seasons. He didn't know this about himself.

5.title: The Phantom Footprints

episode of.title: The Mysteries of Alfred Hedgehog (TV Series 2010– )

5.plot: Huge footprints are everywhere in Gnarly woods. Prized flowers have been crushed. People think it's some giant. It turns out it's Withers the bear, who is starting to fall asleep for the winter and he falls over, crushing things, as he heads toward his den.

6.title: Casting Call

episode of.title: The Mysteries of Alfred Hedgehog (TV Series 2010– )

6.plot: Cynthia is being blamed for making noises during the school play rehearsals - but she insists she said or did nothing of the sort. It turns out a mockingbird is mimicking her.

7.title: The Glowing Eyes

episode of.title: The Mysteries of Alfred Hedgehog (TV Series 2010– )

7.plot: Milo is convinced there are witches when he sees lights, looking like eyes, buzzing around the music teacher's house. Rumors spread and no one shows up to school! After finding clues - Alfred realizes the lights are simply fire flies and no one needs to be afraid.

8.title: The No Treasure Treasure Hunt

episode of.title: The Mysteries of Alfred Hedgehog (TV Series 2010– )

8.plot: Cynthia cheats during a treasure hunt only to discover there is no treasure. Something happened to it and when looking at the final clue - follow the way the sunflowers face - Alfred realizes they changed direction, thus throwing everyone off course.

9.title: A Flash of Silver

episode of.title: The Mysteries of Alfred Hedgehog (TV Series 2010– )

9.plot: Oakly the beaver is really upset. Someone destroyed his damn. Alfred's on the case and discovers that the salmon are spawning and as they swim upstream they're crashing into Oakly damn, destroying his house.

10.title: Buggy Summer

episode of.title: The Mysteries of Alfred Hedgehog (TV Series 2010– )

10.plot: The school picnic is ruined by a swarm of mosquitoes. No one can go outside. Bugs have never been this bad in Gnarly woods. It turns out the bats, who eat all these insects, have been trapped in their cave by a rock slide in the mountains.

11.title: The Case of the Space Invader

episode of.title: The Mysteries of Alfred Hedgehog (TV Series 2010– )

11.plot: Milo swears he saw an invader from outer space. It was foggy and the thing wore a huge mask-helmet. Bees in the area are really weak too. Alfred realizes that it was his father wearing a bee outfit to gather the honey and the fog was the smoke used to make the bees tired.

12.title: The Fur Growing Tree

episode of.title: The Mysteries of Alfred Hedgehog (TV Series 2010– )

12.plot: Mr. Remy thinks he's discovered a new type of tree. It grows Fur! He's blocked the path to the lake until an expert arrives. He's hoping to become famous. Alfred and the others soon discover that it's a moose who is rubbing his fur which is molting due to the advent of summer.

13.title: The Mystery of Old Gnarly

episode of.title: The Mysteries of Alfred Hedgehog (TV Series 2010– )

13.plot: Lily finds Alfred and begs him to save Old Gnarly, the town tree. The tree suddenly went dry and it's set to be cut down. Alfred discovers that some road salt fell on the roots and dehydrated them, hurting the tree.

14.title: Trouble at Turtle Pond

episode of.title: The Mysteries of Alfred Hedgehog (TV Series 2010– )

14.plot: Lugubrious' turtle pond is dry. All the water is gone and it happened practically over night! Alfred discovers that the water source has been diverted by Cynthia to fill up bottles of spring water that she's selling.

imdb.plot outline: In Gnarly Woods, almost anything can happen. A lone bell rings by itself, fish rain from the sky, green eyes glow in the dark, trees turn blue, the lake suddenly foams and is that a giant phantom footprint? Mysteries abound! And Alfred, an energetic ten-year-old, clue collecting detective with a keen eye for detail and an ear for the incongruous finds it all serious mysterious. Alfred has a taste for technology and always carries his amazing Dectectaberry, a high-tech pocket device that records, films, stores multitudinous amounts of information and clues, and collects fingerprints. Sherlock Holmes had Watson and our Master of Mystery Alfred, has his two best buds, Camille and Milo! And anyone can join this skilled and creative detective team. All that's required is critical thinking, a bit of a bent for science, and the ability to link clues... That won't always be easy, but it will always be fun!
imdb.title: The Mysteries of Alfred Hedgehog
plot: An animation series for children, which encourages participation in solving the puzzles and problems of Alfred's marvelously mysterious world.::Penelope Laurence
